nine folios in that MS., but a copy of the missing passage, made by
Dastur Hoshangji Jamaspji from TD2, has been consulted for the purpose
of controlling the Pâz. version of L19.

<span id="fn_224"></span>[41:2](sbe24020.htm#fr_227.md) L19 inserts 'is
good?'

<span id="fn_225"></span>[41:3](sbe24020.htm#fr_228.md) TD2 has 'which is
the friend who is the supremest of friends;' but this does not
correspond well with the reply in § 14.

<span id="fn_226"></span>[41:4](sbe24020.htm#fr_229.md) TD2 adds '*and* are
good.'

